'''爱因斯坦综合症'''（{{lang-en|Einstein syndrome}}）指智力超常的儿童说话能力形成明显晚于正常儿童这一现象，是由[[托马斯·索维尔|托马斯·索维尔]]提出的概念<ref name="Sowell"> {{cite book|first=Thomas|authorlink=Thomas Sowell|last=Sowell|title=The Einstein Syndrome: Bright Children Who Talk Late|url=https://archive.org/details/einsteinsyndrome00sowe|pages=[https://archive.org/details/einsteinsyndrome00sowe/page/89 89]–150|publisher=Basic Books|year=2001|isbn=0-465-08140-1}}</ref>。以[[物理学家|物理学家]][[阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦|阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦]]命名，因爱因斯坦具有此行为特征。其他具有此行为特征的名人还有：{{link-en|约翰·克莱夫·沃德|John Clive Ward}}<ref>{{cite book|last=Close|first=Frank|title=The Infinity Puzzle: Quantum Field Theory and the Hunt for an Orderly Universe|year=2011|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|chapter=Ch. 6, The Identity of John Ward|isbn=9780199593507|authorlink=Frank Close}}</ref>、 [[愛德華·泰勒|愛德華·泰勒]]<ref name="Sowell2003">{{Cite web|title=Ten Years Later by Thomas Sowell|url=https://www.capitalismmagazine.com/2003/05/ten-years-later/|access-date=2022-05-06|date=2003-05-24|last=Sowell|first=Thomas|work=Capitalism Magazine|language=en-US|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130812155442/http://capitalismmagazine.com/2003/05/ten-years-later/|archive-date=2013-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[斯里尼瓦瑟·拉马努金|斯里尼瓦瑟·拉马努金]]<ref name="Sowell2003" />、{{link-en|朱莉娅·罗宾逊|Julia Robinson}}<ref name="Sowell2008">{{Cite book|title=Late-Talking Children|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books/about/Late_Talking_Children.html?id=gJVdNzq8T1cC|publisher=Basic Books|date=2008-08-04|isbn=978-0-7867-2365-2|language=en|first=Thomas|last=Sowell}}</ref>和[[理查德·费曼|理查德·费曼]]<ref name="Sowell2003" /><ref name="Sowell2008" />。另外还有钢琴家[[克拉拉·舒曼|克拉拉·舒曼]]和[[阿图尔·鲁宾斯坦|阿图尔·鲁宾斯坦]]<ref name="Sowell2003" />。

